In a bowl, combine the flour, sesame seeds and salt. Combine the egg and water; stir into dry ingredients just until moistened. In an electric skillet, heat 1 in. of oil to 375 degrees F. Dip chicken into batter. Fry chicken, a few pieces at a time, for 1 to 1-1/2 minutes on each side or until golden brown. Drain on paper towels; keep warm. In a small bowl, combine sauce ingredients. Serve with chicken nuggets.